{
  "stem": "1511.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they don't live through what we will live through because--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The uncle's been taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Finished.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We don't know anything about them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russian took them away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I was hiding, when I was in my girlfriend's house, sleeping over, a few days later, I want to go and see what happened to mine cousin, if she's alive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because with two kids, there's no food, and it's terrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's a very bad situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- so I pick myself up, and I-- I went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went with side streets and things like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was afraid, because where mine cousin used to live, there was a guy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was watching for those people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If he see somebody, right away he reported them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Russian it was called [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was taking care on that section of the people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so when I came up to my cousin, it was on a Friday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was happy that she's alive and the kids, and we start talking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm-- and she was living in a small house, on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm looking through the window, and I see there is two-- two Russian [NON-ENGLISH] over there-- it's like here the MP-- and this guy with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They coming right up the steps for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had washed my head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had very shaggy clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had just a little skirt what I made from a shirt what I took from the house and a little top.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my shoes were just a pair of sandals what I made myself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I saw them coming, I knew they gonna take me, and I'll go where all the other went.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- it's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
